summary: 检测NETGEAR WN604设备中的信息泄露漏洞，该漏洞通过/downloadFile.php文件的参数file导致敏感信息泄露，攻击者可远程获取管理员密码等信息。
summary_en: Detect information disclosure vulnerability in NETGEAR WN604 devices, where the parameter file in /downloadFile.php leads to sensitive information leakage, allowing remote attackers to obtain admin passwords and other details.
